# TLS Certificate Directory
#
# Generate certificates automatically:
#   ./scripts/gen-certs.sh [domain]
#
# Generated files:
#   ca.crt          — Root CA certificate (distribute to clients)
#   ca.key          — Root CA private key (keep secret!)
#   cert.pem        — Server certificate
#   key.pem         — Server private key
#   fullchain.pem   — Server cert + CA chain (use this for Caddy)
#
# All .pem and .crt/.key files are gitignored.
